{"tid":297943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸節目連觀眾都造假 「職業觀眾」價目表曝光","createTime":"2017-06-26T01:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T02:13:40.000Z","uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0d92e5e331866c388017ff8f2cf9337da07378","tid":297943,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:21:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b8%e7%af%80%e7%9b%ae%e9%80%a3%e8%a7%80%e7%9c%be%e9%83%bd%e9%80%a0%e5%81%87-%e3%80%8c%e8%81%b7%e6%a5%ad%e8%a7%80%e7%9c%be%e3%80%8d%e5%83%b9%e7%9b%ae%e8%a1%a8%e6%9b%9d%e5%85%89/ar-BBD4kNc?li=BBqiJuS&amp;OCID=AVRES000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%2599%25b8%25e7%25af%2580%25e7%259b%25ae%25e9%2580%25a3%25e8%25a7%2580%25e7%259c%25be%25e9%2583%25bd%25e9%2580%25a0%25e5%2581%2587-%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%2581%25b7%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e8%25a7%2580%25e7%259c%25be%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%2583%25b9%25e7%259b%25ae%25e8%25a1%25a8%25e6%259b%259d%25e5%2585%2589%2Far-BBD4kNc%3Fli%3DBBqiJuS%26OCID%3DAVRES000&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2673f273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b8%e7%af%80%e7%9b%ae%e9%80%a3%e8%a7%80%e7%9c%be%e9%83%bd%e9%80%a0%e5%81%87-%e3%80%8c%e8%81%b7%e6%a5%ad%e8%a7%80%e7%9c%be%e3%80%8d%e5%83%b9%e7%9b%ae%e8%a1%a8%e6%9b%9d%e5%85%89/ar-BBD4kNc?li=BBqiJuS&amp;OCID=AVRES000</a><br />\n<br />\n出文個果記者係唔係連登仔黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBD4a2J.img?h=1080&amp;w=1920&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=358&amp;y=29\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBD4a2J.img%3Fh%3D1080%26w%3D1920%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D358%26y%3D29&h=1b254f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBD4kNb.img?h=1080&amp;w=1920&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBD4kNb.img%3Fh%3D1080%26w%3D1920%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=1796e617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&copy; 流動新聞 <a href=\"http://news.modia.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e436a327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.modia.com.hk</a> <br />\n近年大陸推出的音樂比賽節目如《我是歌手》（現：歌手）、《中國好聲音》（現：中國新歌聲）、甚至《金曲撈》等均大受好評，除了能夠看到一班歌手或參賽者精湛的演唱外，觀眾的「演出」同樣令人注目，只要細心留意，不難發現觀眾在演唱者演出期間均表現得如癡如醉，甚至誇張到會感動落淚，然而電視機旁的觀眾或網民卻一副「黑人問號」，因為根本找不到要落淚的理由，難道現場聽到的感覺會不一樣？<br />\n<br />\n事實並非如此，皆因於很早以前已經爆出過觀眾都是由製作單位聘請回來的「職業觀眾」，最近更流出這些「職業觀眾」的價目表！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭越多人工越高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸的綜藝節目多不勝數，加上捨得投放資金製作，往往能夠邀請兩岸三地一線的藝人出演節目，競爭自然大，而一眾電視台為了製造節目效果，都會於網上招聘站進行招攬，而最近流出的價目表中寫道「身高 155cm 以上，錄 4 小時一場的節目就有 300 元人民幣的報酬」，若「工作」 4-8 小時的話最多可收到 800 元工資，而職責只需製造氣氛及在台下鼓掌，可謂十分輕鬆！另外據媒體報道則指出，「職業觀眾」的出鏡率會直接影響其收入，事關一次節目裡沒出現幾個鏡頭的話只能拿到 100 元人民幣，表演得最好可獲得 700 至 800 元人民幣，故造成一班觀眾係又喊唔係又喊，最緊要誇張搏上鏡的表現！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民質疑欺騙觀眾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且據業界人士透露自 2014 年起「職業觀眾」市場規模已經高達人民幣 1.8 億元，雖然有網民對這「筍工」表示有興趣，不過亦有網民認為這些「職業觀眾」造成了「台下比台上更專業」的情況，更質疑節目欺騙觀眾。不過說實在，一個比賽節目連觀眾都造假的話，那節目中還有真實的部份嗎？"},{"pid":"3292cfab8e2ee5faa1ac5d80623cf4ce8ee8bbf9","tid":297943,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"所以大家可以留意下 平時啲觀眾好多整容塑化雞<br />\n正常普通睇節目既人冇理由執到咁勁"},{"pid":"a1e044b2e7957294fc6dc0cc77ceb47eb0e079cb","tid":297943,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"其實支那乜柒都假架啦<br />\n<br />\n有乜咁特別呢"},{"pid":"a227c5a0b1acd32795d9bf2369f365295b9f075d","tid":297943,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"個記者提到黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d358acf407d518ea699bc3f9d9dfd1e4034a064","tid":297943,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e99b043fd4fa924839c4ad16365c7829c77bbc","tid":297943,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:53:33.000Z","msg":"每位500<br />\n尖叫加200<br />\n流淚加300<br />\n失禁加1000"},{"pid":"abcbb84e29da825975e4c8283d7107450d3b0432","tid":297943,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每位500<br />\n尖叫加200<br />\n流淚加300<br />\n失禁加1000</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n失禁先得1000 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22eb574a82f04fdffa769bce2eb841a0c1ac0fc","tid":297943,"uid":84,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個記者提到黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}